choices.text: ?A: Definitely the nomination of Kuwait to Unesco for the recognition as heritage city.Q: Finance sector is always recognized as the leading sector in the economy, What are your expectations of Ministry of finance about financial stability in the future?A: The Offer of the State Treasury to investors will be back soon.Q: What have you seen in the last five years is the most important change in the financial sectors?A: The paramount start of the focus on infrastructure and energy.Q: Which vision of the ministry of Finance towards the financial system and how is going to develop?A: The Oil sector revolved significantly during the past years as the backbone of the economy and the other sectors (Tourism, transport, security and administrative) has started to grow, it should follow an economic diversification which includes other sectors to secure the well-being of Kuwait.Q: What are more important challenges that Kuwait has now to compete and come through with?A: Camels are that national contribution which Kuwait always recognized.
